(58, 'New Years in Cape Town 2026', 'new-years-in-cape-town-2026', NULL, 'New Years in Cape Town 2026 is a curated NBGS Travel travel package centered around Cape Town, South Africa. Highlights include 4-Nights in 4* Accommodation, Breakfast daily, Quad biking at the Atlantis Dunes. Travel window: Travel 30 December 2026 to 03 January 2027.', 'New Years in Cape Town 2026 is a curated NBGS Travel package for Cape Town, South Africa. Pricing is per couple. Travel details: Travel 30 December 2026 to 03 January 2027. Package highlights include 4-Nights in 4* Accommodation, Breakfast daily, Quad biking at the Atlantis Dunes, Luxury Day cruise at the Waterfront. Early booking is recommended due to limited availability. You can choose your own date and time for the activities Quad Biking One of the best ways to explore Cape Town''s beautiful natural reserves is from the seat of a quad bike. Experience a super fun ride around 27 square kilometers of pure white sand dunes.', 'Africa', 'South Africa', 'Western Cape', 'Cape Town', 'Cape Town', 'package', 'Couples Package', '4 Nights / 5 Days', '18000.00', 'ZAR', 'per_couple', 'From', '5000.00', 0, NULL, NULL, 1, 'published', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '{"bio":"New Years in Cape Town 2026 is a curated NBGS Travel travel package centered around Cape Town, South Africa. Highlights include 4-Nights in 4* Accommodation, Breakfast daily, Quad biking at the Atlantis Dunes. Travel window: Travel 30 December 2026 to 03 January 2027.","nights":4,"gallery":["/uploads/imported/live-packages/new-years-in-cape-town-2026/00-5-1.jpg"],"excludes":["Flights or transfers to and from Cape Town","Drinks and meals not mentioned","Travel Insurance","R200 per person permit fee to be paid at the Atlantis Dunes"],"includes":["4-Nights in 4* Accommodation","Breakfast daily","Quad biking at the Atlantis Dunes","Luxury Day cruise at the Waterfront"],"dateOfTrip":null,"tripPolicy":"Early booking is recommended due to limited availability.\\nYou can choose 