Africa. Pricing is per couple. Travel details: Travel 30 December 2026 to 03 January 2027. Package highlights include 4-Nights in 4* Accommodation, Breakfast daily, Quad biking at the Atlantis Dunes, Luxury Day cruise at the Waterfront. Early booking is recommended due to limited availability. You can choose your own date and time for the activities Quad Biking One of the best ways to explore Cape Town''s beautiful natural reserves is from the seat of a quad bike. Experience a super fun ride around 27 square kilometers of pure white sand dunes.","mainTripType":"Couples","travelDateLabel":"Travel 30 December 2026 to 03 January 2027","backgroundListingImage":"/uploads/imported/live-packages/new-years-in-cape-town-2026/00-5-1.jpg"}', '2026-04-13 02:26:19', '2026-04-13 02:34:59'),
