st will be\\ncharged\\nCancellations less than 48 hrs prior to arrival, the total cost will be charged\\nNo Shows will be charged at all cost\\nConfirmation & payment:\\nConfirmation is subject to payment and payment must be cleared in full before arrival","youtubeUrl":null,"isLocalTrip":false,"describeTrip":"Visit Zanzibar 2026 is a curated NBGS Travel package for Zanzibar, Tanzania. Pricing is per couple. Travel details: Travel every Saturday between 24 January - 26 March 2026. Package highlights include ✅ 5-Nights Accommodation in 4* Accommodation, ✅ Return flights from Johannesburg to Zanzibar, including airline levy & taxes, ✅ Return airport and hotel transfers, ✅ Daily breakfast. Activity from the below R2000.00 per person : Swimming with turtles and Sunset Cruise Mnemba Island half day( Dolphin & Snorkeling) Prison Island, Stone Town and Spice farm","mainTripType":"Couples","travelDateLabel":"Travel every Saturday between 24 January - 26 March 2026","backgroundListingImage":"/uploads/imported/live-packages/visit-zanzibar-2026/01-222782-zanzibar-jpg-1024x576.webp"}', '2026-04-13 02:26:19', '2026-04-13 02:26:19'),
