,"R200 per person permit fee to be paid at the Atlantis Dunes"],"includes":["2-Nights in 4* Accommodation","Breakfast daily","Quad biking at the dunes","Luxury Day cruise at the Waterfront"],"dateOfTrip":null,"tripPolicy":"This getaway is valid until 15 December 2026, with the flexibility to select your own travel dates.\\nPlease note that a surcharge applies during peak periods, including public holidays and long weekends.\\nCustom date extensions can be arranged upon request and may be subject to additional charges.\\nYou can choose your own date and time for the activities\\nQuad Biking\\nOne of the best ways to explore Cape Town''s beautiful natural reserves is from the seat of a quad bike. Experience a super fun ride around 27 square kilometers of pure white sand dunes.\\nLocation: Atlantis Dunes\\nDuration: 45 Minutes to 1 hour\\nTime: Choice of any time slot from 09:00 to 17:00 departing every hour\\nThe hotel is a 45 minutes drive to the Atlantis Dunes\\nLuxury Day Cruise on a Yacht\\nNothing beats feeling the exhilaration of the open water while taking in panoramic views of the iconic Table Mountain. Along the way, marvel at the vibrant marine life—dolphins may leap joyfully beside you. With the sure beauty of the panoramic scenery this is a \\"must-do\\" when visiting Cape Town.\\nLocation: V&A Waterfront\\nDuration: 1 Hour\\nTime: 11:00 - 12:00 OR 13:00 - 14:00 OR 15:00 - 16:00\\nDrinks and snack are available on the cruise at an additional fee.\\nConfirmation & payment:\\nWe require 50% deposit to secure the package.\\nConfirmation is subject to payment and payment must be cleared in full before arrival.\\nFull payment is required.\\nFull payment must be paid 14 days before date of departure.\\nReservation & Cancellation Policy:\\nWe accept any confirmed cancellation of a reservation. Such cancellation is effective on the day it is received by us. The client will be notified of the acceptance of the cancellation.\\nGenerally, cancellation charges are as followed:\\nUpon confirmation, all payments must be received prior to the arrival of the guests.\\nCancellations between 30 or more prior to arrival, 50% of the total cost will be charged\\nCancellations between 7 days & 48 hrs prior to arrival, 75% of the total cost will be charged\\nCancellations less than 48 hrs prior to arrival, the total cost will be charged\\nNo Shows will be charged at all cost","youtubeUrl":null,"isLocalTrip":true,"describeTrip":"Cape Town Getaway is a curated NBGS Travel package for Cape Town, South Africa. Pricing is per couple. Travel details: Valid Till 15 December 2026. Package highlights include 2-Nights in 4* Accommodation, Breakfast daily, Quad biking at the dunes, Luxury Day cruise at the Waterfront. This getaway is valid until 15 December 2026, with the flexibility to select your own travel dates. Please note that a surcharge applies during peak periods, including public holidays and long weekends. Custom date extensions can be arranged upon request and may be subject to additional charges. You can choose your own date and time for the activities","mainTripType":"Couples","travelDateLabel":"Valid Till 15 December 2026","backgroundListingImage":"/uploads/imported/live-packages/cape-town-getaway/01-img-1371-1024x1015.jpg"}', '2026-04-13 02:26:19', '2026-04-13 02:26:19'),
