(78, 'AFRONATION Portugal 2026', 'afronation-portugal-2026', NULL, 'AFRONATION Portugal 2026 is a curated NBGS Travel group departure centered around Lisbon & Algarve, Portugal. Highlights include 2-Nights 4★ Accommodation in Lisbon, 4-Nights 4★ Accommodation in Algarve, 1-Night 4★ Accommodation in Lisbon. Travel window: 30 JUNE - 07 JULY 2026.', 'AFRONATION Portugal 2026 is a curated NBGS Travel package for Lisbon & Algarve, Portugal. Pricing is per person sharing. Travel details: 30 JUNE - 07 JULY 2026. Package highlights include 2-Nights 4★ Accommodation in Lisbon, 4-Nights 4★ Accommodation in Algarve, 1-Night 4★ Accommodation in Lisbon, Return flights from Johannesburg to Lisbon, Return airport transfers. A R3000 non-refundable deposit is required to secure your booking. Travel dates are fixed for 30 June – 07 July 2026. Prices are per person sharing. To upgrade to a single room will be R15 000.00.', 'Europe', 'Portugal', 'Lisbon', 'Lisbon & Algarve', 'Lisbon & Algarve', 'group_trip', 'Group Trip', '7 Nights / 8 Days', '45000.00', 'ZAR', 'per_person_sharing', 'From', '3000.00', 1, '2026-06-30', '2026-07-07', 1, 'published', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '{"bio":"AFRONATION Portugal 2026 is a curated NBGS Travel group departure centered around Lisbon & Algarve, Portugal. Highlights include 2-Nights 4★ Accommodation in Lisbon, 4-Nights 4★ Accommodation in Algarve, 1-Night 4★ Accommodation in Lisbon. Travel window: 30 JUNE - 07 JULY 2026.","nights":7,"gallery":["/uploads/imported/live-packages/afronation-portugal-2026/01-afro-nation-portugal-2025-5384212-822x1024.jpg","/uploads/imported/live-packages/afronation-portugal-2026/02-0527-1126-portimao-1024x683.jpg","/uploads/imported/live-packages/afronation-portugal-2026/03-freguesia-de-estrela-txasbfxszne-unsplash-683x1024.jpg","/uploads/imported/live-packages/afronation-portugal-2026/04-dsc04503-768x512.jpg","/uploads/imported/live-packages/afronation-portugal-2026/05-praia-marinha-beach-lagoa-algarve-1024x683.jpg","/up