(81, 'Discover Thailand 2026', 'discover-thailand-2026', NULL, 'Discover Thailand 2026 is a curated NBGS Travel group departure centered around Bangkok & Phuket, Thailand. Highlights include ✅ Return flights from Johannesburg to Bangkok & Phuket, ✅ 2-Nights Accommodation in Bangkok, ✅ 5-Nights Accommodation in Phuket. Travel window: 24 September - 02 October 2026 Or Choose Own Dates.', 'Discover Thailand 2026 is a curated NBGS Travel package for Bangkok & Phuket, Thailand. Pricing is per person sharing. Travel details: 24 September - 02 October 2026 Or Choose Own Dates. Package highlights include ✅ Return flights from Johannesburg to Bangkok & Phuket, ✅ 2-Nights Accommodation in Bangkok, ✅ 5-Nights Accommodation in Phuket, ✅ Return airport-hotel transfers, ✅ Breakfast daily. A non-refundable deposit of R5000 is required to secure your booking. The package can be paid off in 6 monthly installments of R5500. The price is based on per person sharing — single supplement available. Travel insurance is strongly recommended. Activities and meals not listed are excluded.', 'Asia', 'Thailand', 'Bangkok', 'Bangkok & Phuket', 'Bangkok & Phuket', 'group_trip', 'Group Trip', '7 Nights / 8 Days', '32000.00', 'ZAR', 'per_person_sharing', 'From', '5000.00', 0, NULL, NULL, 1, 'published', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '{"bio":"Discover Thailand 2026 is a curated NBGS Travel group departure centered around Bangkok & Phuket, Thailand. Highlights include ✅ Return flights from Johannesburg to Bangkok & Phuket, ✅ 2-Nights Accommodation in Bangkok, ✅ 5-Nights Accommodation in Phuket. Travel window: 24 September - 02 October 2026 Or Choose Own Dates.","nights":7,"gallery":["/uploads/imported/live-packages/discover-thailand-2026/01-screenshot-239-768x419.png","/uploads/imported/live-packages/discover-thailand-2026/02-screenshot-240-600x391.png","/uploads/imported/live-packages/discover-thailand-2026/03-screenshot-241-1024x368.png"],"excludes":["Medical and travel insurance","All personal items