(82, 'Visit Spain 2026', 'visit-spain-2026', NULL, 'Visit Spain 2026 is a curated NBGS Travel travel package centered around Barcelona, Spain. Highlights include ✅ Return flights from Johannesburg, ✅ 4-Nights Accommodation in Barcelona, ✅ 3-Nights Accommodation in Ibiza. Travel window: April | May | June |September.', 'Visit Spain 2026 is a curated NBGS Travel package for Barcelona, Spain. Pricing is per person sharing. Travel details: April | May | June |September. Package highlights include ✅ Return flights from Johannesburg, ✅ 4-Nights Accommodation in Barcelona, ✅ 3-Nights Accommodation in Ibiza, ✅ 2-Nights Accommodation in Madrid, ✅ Return airport & domestic transfers. A non-refundable deposit is required to secure your booking. Full payment must be made prior to travel. The package is based on per person sharing, with single supplement options available. Travel insurance is not included and is strongly recommended. Meals and optional activities not mentioned in the package are excluded. Visa assistance is available upon request. All personal expenses are the responsibility of the traveler.', 'Europe', 'Spain', 'Catalonia', 'Barcelona', 'Barcelona', 'package', 'Travel Package', '9 Nights / 10 Days', '50000.00', 'ZAR', 'per_person_sharing', 'From', '5001.00', 0, NULL, NULL, 1, 'published', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '{"bio":"Visit Spain 2026 is a curated NBGS Travel travel package centered around Barcelona, Spain. Highlights include ✅ Return flights from Johannesburg, ✅ 4-Nights Accommodation in Barcelona, ✅ 3-Nights Accommodation in Ibiza. Travel window: April | May | June |September.","nights":9,"gallery":["/uploads/imported/live-packages/visit-spain-2026/01-aa5231d66880b52a4ad043b59d1585b2-1024x683.jpg","/uploads/imported/live-packages/visit-spain-2026/02-spain-balearic-islands-mallorca-cala-mesquida-600x400.jpg"],"excludes":["Package Excludes","Medical and travel insurance","Visa fees (Visa assistance available)","Meals and drinks not mentioned"],"includes":