(86, 'Visit Zanzibar 2026', 'visit-zanzibar-2026-2', NULL, 'Visit Zanzibar 2026 is a curated NBGS Travel travel package centered around Zanzibar, Tanzania. Highlights include ✅ 5-Nights Accommodation in 4* Accommodation, ✅ Return flights from Johannesburg to Zanzibar, including airline levy & taxes, ✅ Return airport and hotel transfers. Travel window: Choose Own Travel Dates.', 'Visit Zanzibar 2026 is a curated NBGS Travel package for Zanzibar, Tanzania. Pricing is per person sharing. Travel details: Choose Own Travel Dates. Package highlights include ✅ 5-Nights Accommodation in 4* Accommodation, ✅ Return flights from Johannesburg to Zanzibar, including airline levy & taxes, ✅ Return airport and hotel transfers, ✅ Daily breakfast, ✅ Tours: Stonetown, Spice Tour, Prison Island, Safari Blue, Nungwi Turtles. Trip Policy & Conditions A non-refundable deposit of R5,000.00 is required to secure your booking. Full payment must be completed before the travel dates to confirm your reservation. Accommodation is based on shared rooms. Single supplement rates are available upon request.', 'Africa', 'Tanzania', 'Zanzibar Urban West', 'Zanzibar', 'Zanzibar', 'package', 'Travel Package', '5 Nights / 6 Days', '23000.00', 'ZAR', 'per_person_sharing', 'From', '5000.00', 0, NULL, NULL, 1, 'published', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '{"bio":"Visit Zanzibar 2026 is a curated NBGS Travel travel package centered around Zanzibar, Tanzania. Highlights include ✅ 5-Nights Accommodation in 4* Accommodation, ✅ Return flights from Johannesburg to Zanzibar, including airline levy & taxes, ✅ Return airport and hotel transfers. Travel window: Choose Own Travel Dates.","nights":5,"gallery":["/uploads/imported/live-packages/visit-zanzibar-2026-2/01-soi-romanee-phuket-old-town-1024x682.jpg","/uploads/imported/live-packages/visit-zanzibar-2026-2/02-ko-phi-phi-island-jpg-768x576.webp","/uploads/imported/live-packages/visit-zanzibar-2026-2/03-jumeirah-muscat-bay-exterior-7-jpg.avif","/uploads/imported/live-p