king. Full payment must be completed before the travel dates to confirm your reservation. Accommodation is based on shared rooms. Single supplement rates are available upon request.","mainTripType":"Package","travelDateLabel":"Choose Own Travel Dates","backgroundListingImage":"/uploads/imported/live-packages/visit-zanzibar-2026-2/01-soi-romanee-phuket-old-town-1024x682.jpg"}', '2026-04-13 02:26:19', '2026-04-13 02:26:19'),
(87, 'Discover Italy 2026', 'discover-italy-2026', NULL, 'Discover Italy 2026 is a curated NBGS Travel travel package centered around Rome, Italy. Highlights include ✅ Return flights from Johannesburg to Italy, ✅ 2-Nights Accommodation in Milan, ✅ 1-Night Accommodation in Venice. Travel window: Choose own dates between April | May | September | October.', 'Discover Italy 2026 is a curated NBGS Travel package for Rome, Italy. Pricing is per person sharing. Travel details: Choose own dates between April | May | September | October. Package highlights include ✅ Return flights from Johannesburg to Italy, ✅ 2-Nights Accommodation in Milan, ✅ 1-Night Accommodation in Venice, ✅ 3-Nights Accommodation in Rome, ✅ Return airport transfers. A non-refundable deposit of R5000 is required to secure your booking. Accommodation is based on shared rooms, with additional charges for single occupancy. A Schengen visa is required for travel, and visa assistance is provided. Travel insurance is not included and should be purchased separately. Meals and drinks not specified are excluded, as well as any optional activities.', 'Europe', 'Italy', 'Lazio', 'Rome', 'Rome', 'package', 'Travel Package', '6 Nights / 7 Days', '41000.00', 'ZAR', 'per_person_sharing', 'From', '5000.00', 0, NULL, NULL, 1, 'published', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '{"bio":"Discover Italy 2026 is a curated NBGS Travel travel package centered around Rome, Italy. Highlights include ✅ Return flights from Johannesburg to Italy, ✅ 2-Nights Accommodation in Milan, ✅ 1-Night Accommodation in Venice. Travel window: Choose own dates between April | May | September | October.","nights":6,"gallery":["/uploads/imported/live-packages/discover-italy-2026/01-milan-italy-bi-1-1024x576.jpg","/uploads/imported/live-packages/discover-italy-2026/02-manarola-istock-freeartist-www-istockphoto-1024x682-1-768x512.jpg"],"excludes":["Schengen Visa (we provide assistance)","Medical and travel insurance (highly recommended)","*Meals and drinks not mentioned in the itinerary","*Personal expenses and optional activities"],"includes":["✅ Return flights from Johannesburg to Italy","✅ 2-Nights Accommodation in Milan","✅ 1-Night Accommodation in Venice","✅ 3-Nights Accommodation in Rome","✅ Return airport transfers","✅ Domestic Transfers (Train Tickets)","✅ Daily breakfast","✅ Pompeii, Amalfi & Positano Tour (Can be substituted for Tuscany & wine tasting with lunch tour)","✅ Visa assistance"],"dateOfTrip":null,"tripPolicy":"A non-refundable deposit of R5000 is required to secure your booking. Accommodation is based on shared rooms, with additional charges for single occupancy.\\nA Schengen visa is required for travel, and visa assistance is provided.\\nTravel insurance is not included and should be purchased separately. Meals and drinks not specified are excluded, as well as any optional activities.","youtubeUrl":null,"isLocalTrip":false,"describeTrip":"Discover Italy 2026 is a curated NBGS Travel package for Rome, Italy. Pricing is per person sharing. Travel details: Choose own dates between April | May | September | October. Package highlights include ✅ Return flights from Johannesburg to Italy, ✅ 2-Nights Accommodation in Milan, ✅ 1-Night Accommodation in Venice, ✅ 3-Nights Accommodation in Rome, ✅ Return airport transfers. A non-refundable deposit of R5000 is required to secure your booking. Accommodation is based on shared rooms, with additional charges for single occupancy. A Schengen visa is required for travel, and visa assistance is provided. Travel insurance is not included and should be purchased separately. Meals and drinks not specified are excluded, as well as any optional activities.","mainTripType":"Package","travelDateLabel":"Choose own dates between April | May | September | October","backgroundListingImage":"/uploads/imported/live-packages/discover-italy-2026/01-milan-italy-bi-1-1024x576.jpg"}', '2026-04-13 02:26:19', '2026-04-13 02:26:19'),
(88, 'Discover Greece 2026', 'discover-greece-2026', NULL, 'Discover Greece 2026 is a curated NBGS Travel travel package centered around Athens, Greece. Highlights include ✅ Return flights from Johannesburg to Athens, ✅ 2-Nights Accommodation in Athens, ✅ 3-Night Accommodation in Santorini. Travel window: Choose own dates between April | May | September | October.', 'Discover Greece 2026 is a curated NBGS Travel package for Athens, Greece. Pricing is per person sharing. Travel details: Choose own dates between April | May | September | October. Package highlights include ✅ Return flights from Johannesburg to Athens, ✅ 2-Nights Accommodation in Athens, ✅ 3-Night Accommodation in Santorini, ✅ 2-Nights Accommodation in Mykonos, ✅ Return airport transfers. To ensure a smooth and enjoyable experience, please review our trip policy. A R5000 non-refundable deposit is required to secure your spot. a The deposit is non-refundable under any circumstances, and if you cancel after full payment, any refunds (if applicable) will be subject to supplier policies and cancellation fees. For travel requirements, a valid passport with at least six months’ validity beyond travel dates is required. A Schengen Visa is mandatory for entry into Greece, and while we provide assistance with the application process, approval is at the discretion of the relevant embassy. We also strongly recommend travel and medical insurance for your peace of mind. By booking this trip, you agree to the terms and conditions outlined in this policy. If you have any questions, feel free to reach out—we’re here to help make your trip stress-free and unforgettable!', 'Europe', 'Greece', 'Attica', 'Athens', 'Athens', 'package', 'Travel Package', '7 Nights / 8 Days', '44000.00', 'ZAR', 'per_person_sharing', 'From', '5000.00', 0, NULL, NULL, 1, 'published', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '{"bio":"Discover Greece 2026 is a curated NBGS Travel travel package centered around Athens, Greece. Highlights include ✅ Return flights from Johannesburg to Athens, ✅ 2-Nights Accommodation in Athens, ✅ 3-Night Accommodation in Santorini. Travel window: Choose own dates between April | May | September | October.","nights":7,"gallery":["/uploads/imported/live-packages/discover-greece-2026/01-gettyimages-773131123-5c27f7c346e0fb000179ee94-1024x680.jpg","/uploads/imported/live-packages/discover-greece-2026/02-intrepid-travel-greece-mykonos-tavern-by-sea-2-1024x684.jpg","/uploads/imported/live-packages/discover-greece-2026/03-05-parthenonacropolis-38687611-1-768x512.webp"],"excludes":["Schengen Visa (we provide assistance)","Medical and travel insurance (highly recommended)","Meals and drinks not mentioned in the itinerary","Personal expenses and optional activities"],"includes":["✅ Return flights from Johannesburg to Athens","✅ 2-Nights Accommodation in Athens","✅ 3-Night Accommodation in Santorini","✅ 2-Nights Accommodation in Mykonos","✅ Return airport transfers","✅ Domestic Transfers (Ferry)","✅ Daily breakfast","✅ Athen City Tour","✅ Santorini Cruise with BBQ","✅ Visa assistance"],"dateOfTrip":null,"tripPolicy":"To ensure a smooth and enjoyable experience, please review our trip policy. A R5000 non-refundable deposit is required to secure your spot. a\\nThe deposit is non-refundable under any circumstances, and if you cancel after full payment, any refunds (if applicable) will be subject to supplier policies and cancellation fees.\\nFor travel requirements, a valid passport with at least six months’ validity beyond travel dates is required. A Schengen Visa is mandatory for entry into Greece, and while we provide assistance with the application process, approval is at the discretion of the relevant embassy. We also strongly recommend travel and medical insurance for your peace of mind.\\nBy booking this trip, you agree to the terms and conditions outlined in this policy. If you have any questions, feel free to reach out—we’re here to help make your trip stress-free and unforgettable!","youtubeUrl":null,"isLocalTrip":false,"describeTrip":"Discover Greece 2026 is a curated NBGS Travel package for Athens, Greece. Pricing is per person sharing. Travel details: Choose own dates between April | May | September | October. Package highlights include ✅ Return flights from Johannesburg to Athens, ✅ 2-Nights Accommodation in Athens, ✅ 3-Night Accommodation in Santorini, ✅ 2-Nights Accommodation in Mykonos, ✅ Return airport transfers. To ensure a smooth and enjoyable experience, please review our trip policy. A R5000 non-refundable deposit is required to secure your spot. a The deposit is non-refundable under any circumstances, and if you cancel after full payment, any refunds (if applicable) will be subject to supplier policies and cancellation fees. For travel requirements, a valid passport with at least six months’ validity beyond travel dates is required. A Schengen Visa is mandatory for entry into Greece, and while we provide assistance with the application process, approval is at the discretion of the relevant embassy. We also strongly recommend travel and medical insurance for your peace of mind. By booking this trip, you agree to the terms and conditions outlined in this policy. If you have any questions, feel free to reach out—we’re here to help make your trip stress-free and unforgettable!","mainTripType":"Package","travelDateLabel":"Choose own dates between April | May | September | October","backgroundListingImage":"/uploads/imported/live-packages/discover-greece-2026/01-gettyimages-773131123-5c27f7c346e0fb000179ee94-1024x680.jpg"}', '2026-04-13 02:26:19', '2026-04-13 02:26:19');
